    <!-- Privacy Policy -->
    <string name="privacy_policy_title">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_heading">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_text">\nVersion 1.1\nLast updated: April 15, 2026\n\n1. Data Storage\nAll your credential data is stored locally on your device using an encrypted database. We do not have access to your passwords or any personal information stored within the app.\n\n2. Backup and Restore\nThe app provides a manual backup and restore feature. When you choose to export a backup, your data is converted to a JSON file stored in the device\'s cache directory, then sent as an email attachment. To restore, you select a previously exported backup file from your device to import. The entire backup and restore process is fully user-initiated, and no data is uploaded to any cloud server.\n\n3. Biometric Data\nThe app may use biometric authentication (fingerprint) for login. Biometric data is processed by your device\'s secure hardware and is never stored or transmitted by this app.\n\n4. Data Collection\nThis app does not collect, transmit, or share any personal data with third parties. All data remains on your device unless you explicitly choose to export a backup file via email.\n\n5. Security\nWe use industry-standard security practices including PBKDF2 password hashing and automatic session timeout to protect your data.\n\n6. Contact\nIf you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact the developer.</string>
